# Multimedia - Radar image of Christmas Island
<img src="https://www.dlr.de/en/images/2013/1/terrasar-x-image-of-christmas-island_8506/@@images/image-1000-0acec99c3dbed4f4948880ace87eba2f.jpeg" 
